ad_text: Northwest Regional Education Service District - Official Sponsored Unique opportunity for Registered Nurses (RNs) and Licensed Practical Nurses (LPNs): Work at one of our Outdoor School sites starting February 16 until early June. Contribute to this quintessential experience for Oregon students. Students in Outdoor School receive an exciting environmental education and explore their surroundings (mountains, forests, streams, and fields). Ideal candidates love working outside and working with kids. Recent graduates are encouraged to apply. Visit our website ( nwresd.org/careers ) to learn more about working with us, or apply directly at the links below. Apply for an RN position: https://phl.applitrack.com/nwresd/onlineapp/default.aspx?Category=NW+Outdoor+Science+School&AppliTrackJobId=2606&AppliTrackLayoutMode=detail&AppliTrackViewPosting=1 Apply for an LPN position: https://phl.applitrack.com/nwresd/onlineapp/JobPostings/view.asp?Category=NW+Outdoor+Science+School&AppliTrackJobId=2660&AppliTrackLayoutMode=detail&AppliTrackViewPosting=1 Northwest Regional Education Service District - Official School Send message
